quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,is waqt tum mein se do jamaaton ne jee chore dena chaha magar khuda un ka madadgaar tha aur mominoun ko khuda hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye
  3,123,aur khuda ne jang-e badar mein bhi tumhari madad ki thi aur is waqt bhi tum be saro vsaman they pas khuda se daro ( aur un ehsaanon ko yaad karo ) taakay shukar karo
  3,124,jab tum mominoun se yeh keh ( kar un ke dil barha ) rahay they kekiya yeh kaafi nahi ke perwar-digaar teen hazaar farishtay nazil kar ke tumhe madad day
  3,125,haan agar tum dil ko mazboot rakho aur ( khuda se ) drtay raho aur kafir tum par josh ke sath دفعتہ hamla kar dein to perwar-digaar paanch hazaar farishtay jin par nishaan hon ge tumhari madad ko beje ga
  3,126,aur is madad ko khuda ne tumhare liyezarya basharat banaya yani is liye ke tumahray dilon ko is se tasalii haasil ho warna madad to khuda hi ki hai jo ghalib ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  3,127,( yeh khuda ne ) is liye (kiya ) ke kafiroon ki aik jamaat ko halaak ya inhen zaleel o maghloob kar day ke ( jaisay aeye they waisay hi ) nakaam wapas jayen
  3,128,( ae paighambar ) is kaam mein tumhara kuch ikhtiyar nahi ( ab do soorten hain ) ya khuda unkay haal par meharbani kere ya inhen azaab day ke yeh zalim log hain
  3,129,aur jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai woh jisay chahay bakhash day aur jisay chahay azaab kere aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  3,130,ae imaan walo! dugna chuguna sood nah khao aur khuda se daro taakay nijaat haasil karo
  3,131,aur ( dozakh ki ) aag se bachcho jo kafiroon ke liye tayyar ki gayi hai
  3,132,aur khuda aur is ke rasool ki itaat karo taakay tum par rehmat ki jaye
